<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>How It Works</title>

  <!-- Geist Font -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@100..900&family=Noto+Sans:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    body {
      background: #f2f2f2;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Geist', system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    .a4-page {
      width: 491px;
      height: 694px;
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      position: relative;
    }

    .inner-div {
      width: 451px;
      height: 654px;
      border: 2px solid #caa46a;
      padding: 20px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Corner Logo */
    .corner-logo {
      width: 14px;
      position: absolute;
      top: 18px;
      right: 18px;
    }

    /* Title */
    .title {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #7A542A;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    /* Flow Layout */
    .flow {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .step {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    /* Black Diamond */
    .diamond {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      background: black;
      transform: rotate(45deg);
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .content {
      flex: 1;
    }

    /* Gold Heading Bar */
    .heading {
      background: #EFCE8D;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 6px 15px;
      clip-path: polygon(0 0, 95% 0, 100% 50%, 95% 100%, 0 100%, 3% 50%);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .step p {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* Flow Arrow */
    .flow-arrow {
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    /* Background Illustration */
    .bg-illustration {
      width: 451px;
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      opacity: 0.1;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      font-size: 10px;
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 5px;
      left: 20px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="a4-page">
  <div class="inner-div">

    <img src="/images/R.svg" class="corner-logo" alt="Royal Logo">

    <h1 class="title">HOW IT WORKS?</h1>

    <div class="flow">

      <div class="step">
        <div class="diamond"></div>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="heading">ONBOARDING</div>
          <p>Simple onboarding with clear terms, timelines, and revenue expectations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <img src="/images/arrow.svg" class="flow-arrow" alt="arrow">

      <div class="step">
        <div class="diamond"></div>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="heading">LICENSING</div>
          <p>We handle all holiday home permits and compliance requirements.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <img src="/images/arrow.svg" class="flow-arrow" alt="arrow">

      <div class="step">
        <div class="diamond"></div>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="heading">SETUP</div>
          <p>Professional setup to maximize guest appeal and booking potential.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <img src="/images/arrow.svg" class="flow-arrow" alt="arrow">

      <div class="step">
        <div class="diamond"></div>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="heading">LISTING & PRICING</div>
          <p>Your property is listed across top platforms with demand-based pricing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <img src="/images/arrow.svg" class="flow-arrow" alt="arrow">

      <div class="step">
        <div class="diamond"></div>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="heading">OPERATIONS</div>
          <p>End-to-end guest handling, housekeeping, and maintenance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <img src="/images/arrow.svg" class="flow-arrow" alt="arrow">

      <div class="step">
        <div class="diamond"></div>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="heading">REVENUE MANAGEMENT</div>
          <p>Continuous performance tracking with transparent monthly reports.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <img src="/images/arrow.svg" class="flow-arrow" alt="arrow">

      <div class="step">
        <div class="diamond"></div>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="heading">MONTHLY PAYOUT</div>
          <p>Net earnings transferred directly to you every month.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <img src="/images/illustration.png" class="bg-illustration" alt="illustration">

  </div>

  <div class="footer">Confidential Â© Royal Holiday Homes</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
